name: PARIS PANAME dresser
description: Designed by Bruno Moinard. A specialist in luxury boutiques and hotels, Bruno Moinard has created a complete two-faceted collection for Roche Bobois: the first plays on reassuring thickness and roundness, while the second focuses on geometric precision. The refinement of details and materials are their common feature. These pieces of furniture are in sync with the times and can be combined with both classic and modern styles. This unit is robust and woody; its shapes are winding and soft.
